OL,6,FA man who threw a chair at riot police
OL,7,Fand another who claimed he was too
OL,8,Fdrunk to remember what he had done
OL,9,Fhave been jailed for their parts in
OL,10,Ftrouble in Rotherham.
OL,12,FMorgan Hardy, 29, of Melton High
OL,13,FStreet, Rotherham, also threw fence
OL,14,Fpanels and a fire extinguisher during
OL,15,Fthe disorder outside the Holiday Inn
OL,16,FExpress on 4 August.
