OL,3,C'Family man' threw chair, fencing and
OL,4,Cfire extinguisher at riot police
OL,6,FSheffield Crown Court heard he was
OL,7,Fpart of a group shouting "we want our
OL,8,Fcountry back" when a mob besieged the
OL,9,Fhotel, where more than 200 asylum
OL,10,Fseekers were being housed.
OL,12,FHe could be seen on body-worn camera
OL,13,Ffootage at the front of the crowd,
OL,14,Ftaunting officers with his arms
OL,15,Foutstretched.
OL,17,FJudge Sarah Wright was told that,
OL,18,Fafter his arrest, he asked police if
OL,19,Fthe "immigrants" had all gone from the
OL,20,Fhotel.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
