OL,3,C'Family man' threw chair, fencing and
OL,4,Cfire extinguisher at riot police
OL,6,FWhen told that they had been moved, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "Good. No more women and
OL,8,Fchildren will be hurt."
OL,10,FRebecca Tanner, mitigating, said he
OL,11,Fwas a hard-working family man who only
OL,12,Fwent to the hotel to be nosey but
OL,13,Fended up doing something he admitted
OL,14,Fwas "deplorable".
OL,16,FShe said: "He has brought shame on
OL,17,Fhimself and shame on his family."
OL,19,FHardy was jailed for three years.
