OL,6,FCharlie Eames, of High Street,
OL,7,FSheffield, was also jailed in
OL,8,Fconnection with the same incident.
OL,10,FBody-worn camera footage showed Eames
OL,11,Fat the front of the crowd with no
OL,12,Fshirt, but wearing a padded gillet and
OL,13,Fwith a bottle of alcohol pushed down
OL,14,Fhis waistband.
OL,16,FWhen prosecutor Neil Coxon suggested
OL,17,Fthis was a bottle of beer, Eames
OL,18,Fcorrected him over the prison
OL,19,Fvideolink, stating it was a bottle of
OL,20,FStones Ginger Wine.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
