OL,3,C'Family man' threw chair, fencing and
OL,4,Cfire extinguisher at riot police
OL,6,FThe footage showed Eames throwing an
OL,7,Funknown object at the line of riot
OL,8,Fshields and then encouraging another
OL,9,Fman in a mask to throw a large piece
OL,10,Fof wood at officers.
OL,12,FMs Tanner, who was also representing
OL,13,FEames, said her client was an
OL,14,Falcoholic, had drunk a substantial
OL,15,Famount before the incident captured on
OL,16,Fvideo, and could not remember throwing
OL,17,Fthe object, which the court heard
OL,18,Fcould have been a branch.
