OL,3,C'Family man' threw chair, fencing and
OL,4,Cfire extinguisher at riot police
OL,6,FShe said Eames, who admitted violent
OL,7,Fdisorder, had seen the protest
OL,8,Fhappening outside the hotel on TikTok
OL,9,Fbefore it turned violent and decided
OL,10,Fgo along, believing it to be
OL,11,F"peaceful".
OL,13,FMs Tanner told the court: "He readily
OL,14,Faccepts he was highly intoxicated."
OL,16,FShe added: "When the mood shifted, he
OL,17,Fbecame a willing participant."
OL,19,FEames was jailed for two-and-a-half
OL,20,Fyears.
