OL,6,FAlso on Thursday, father-of-five
OL,7,FCameron Callear, 30, of Orchard Way,
OL,8,FThurnscoe, was jailed for two years
OL,9,Fand 10 months for his part in the
OL,10,Fdisorder.
OL,12,FFootage shown in court showed Callear
OL,13,Fkicking out at police riot shields and
OL,14,Fthen breaking the leg off a chair
OL,15,Fwhich had been brought out of the
OL,16,Fhotel.
OL,18,FThe defendant was then seen to throw
OL,19,Fthe leg at police lines as another man
OL,20,Flaunched the remains of the chair at
OL,21,Fofficers.
